In addition to these platforms, employing a strategic approach will significantly improve your chances of finding the right role. A key tip is to use precise filters on these websites; be sure to set the location filter to "Oman," "Dubai," or "UAE" while also selecting the "Remote" or "Work From Home" option to pinpoint roles that are both based in your target region and can be performed from another country.
